We can use snd_soc_dai_link_component to specify codec_conf.
Let's use it.

Signed-off-by: Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/878snh59j1.wl-kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com
